## Visual Style

### Color Palette:
- Primary: Deep, muted navy (#23212A)
- Secondary: Warm sand beige (#ECE1D4)
- Accent: Bronze-gold (#A97C50)
- Text: Soft white (#F8F6F3); body text on light backgrounds: deep charcoal (#3A3732)
- Details: Subtle gradients with sunset mauves (#B49587 to #23212A) and soft blush (#D1B7A1)
- Combinations: Light beige on deep navy; bronze-gold buttons on light/dark backgrounds; muted warmth

### Typography & Layout:
- Font Family: Headlines with Playfair Display (or similar serif); body/UI with Inter/Lato
- Weight & Hierarchy: Bold/semibold headlines/CTAs; regular/light body
- Alignment: Centered hero with CTA; left-aligned content sections if any
- Spacing: 40–80px vertical spacing between sections; 24–32px internal padding
- Typography Treatments: Large headlines; uppercase section labels; italic or lighter secondary info

### Key Design Elements

#### Card Design:
- Radius: 8–12px
- Borders: Thin, light beige or translucent white
- Hover: Slight scale-up with bronze-gold accent
- Visual Hierarchy: Large image at top, bold title, details and actions below

#### Navigation:
- Top navbar over hero; becomes solid on scroll
- Minimal links, generous spacing
- Active state: Bronze-gold underline
- Mobile: Hamburger with slide-out

#### Data Visualization:
- Not applicable for this page; style guidance kept for consistency

#### Interactive Elements:
- Buttons: Bronze-gold fill (#A97C50); white or navy text; secondary beige with bronze outline
- Focus: Clear focus ring in accent color
- Hover/Feedback: Subtle, uplifting micro-interactions

### Design Philosophy
- Modern luxury editorial aesthetic: calm, refined, warm.
- Clear hierarchy and high-touch feel; no clutter.
- Visual storytelling with tasteful imagery and typography.
- Serene, intuitive, and trust-building experience.

